streaming platform notes
 - Try to make Simulation like a real network traffic and try to recreate the issues.
 - Exponential backoff - ceiling - will decide how much to put burst
 - Feature flags - based on OS, based on version, based on region
 - Degradation scenario 
 - Multiple CDN - Based on anticipated network traffic calculation precautionary preparation takes place.
 - Back of the envelope calculation for prescaling
 - Cache offloading is the major thing to improve performance as well and money saving option to avoid lot of request going from CDN to APP server to db server.
 - Use of load balancer   
 - 3 stacks of cache, video, image, text data
